      { name: "Prostaglandin E1 (Alprostadil)", type: "Vasodilator", action: "Maintains ductus arteriosus patency to allow pulmonary blood flow in severe cases", sideEffects: "Apnea (10-12%), hypotension, fever", contra: "None absolute in emergent situations", pearl: "Used in neonates with severe pulmonary stenosis who are duct-dependent for pulmonary blood flow. Keep intubation equipment at bedside." }
